Sharyn Hodgson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharyn_Hodgson 0 Sharyn Hodgson (born 25 August 1968) is a former Australian actress, best known for playing the role of original character of troubled teenager Carly Morris (later Luccini) in the popular soap opera, Home and Away (1988–91); with subsequent guest appearances reprising the part until 2008.
